This is readme page

In python environment check your pip version

Environment at python 3.6.12

Get requirement package with internet connect

pip install - r requirements.txt

cd code

python Project2_ImageStitching.py --img_folder ../data/ --num_intervals 2 --contrast_threshold 0.1 --focal_length 1600 --resize_ratio 3 --crop True

will get image stitching result

Or you can set up paramteres to fit your images requirements

**Notice Please follow image stitching order to rename your pictures in data folder! 資料夾照片命名請依照影像拼接順序依序命名

